snippet.title: Oliver and Mom Kids Story about sweet machine
snippet.description:
In this fun kids story, Oliver helps his mom with the housework so that the buttons on the sweet machines start working. 

Kids will love learning about Oliver and Mom in this sweet story about teamwork and how working together can help solve problems.
